OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson says doctor told him
OL,4,Cto stop working after heart procedure
OL,6,FJeremy Clarkson has said his doctor
OL,7,Ftold him to stop working following a
OL,8,Fheart procedure.
OL,10,FThe presenter, who is a host of ITV's
OL,11,FWho Wants To Be A Millionaire? and
OL,12,FPrime Video's Clarkson's Farm, was
OL,13,Frecently fitted with two stents, which
OL,14,Fimproves blood flow to the heart.
OL,16,FIn The Sun, he said that his doctor
OL,17,Ftold him "a lot" of his current work
OL,18,Fwill have "to go", and suggested
OL,19,Freplacing it with golf.
