OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson says doctor told him
OL,4,Cto stop working after heart procedure
OL,6,FClarkson added: "If I didn't work, I'd
OL,7,Fjust sit at home all day, rotting.
OL,9,F"The worst problem though is diet. To
OL,10,Fcut my alarmingly high levels of
OL,11,Fcholesterol, I need to cut out,
OL,12,Fcompletely, everything I like eating.
OL,14,F"Bacon, sausages, beef, lamb, pork,
OL,15,Fbutter, chips, proper milk, Cadbury's
OL,16,Ffruit and nut bars and the interesting
OL,17,Fbit in an egg.
OL,19,F"I've had a week now to live in the
OL,20,Fnew regime and it's horrific."
