OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson says doctor told him
OL,4,Cto stop working after heart procedure
OL,6,FHowever, he dismissed the idea of
OL,7,Fstopping work, saying he would "carry
OL,8,Fon" and just change his diet.
OL,10,FThe former Top Gear presenter, who has
OL,11,Fa brewery, farm shop and pub in
OL,12,FOxfordshire, also says he has been
OL,13,Ftold to shift towards eating
OL,14,Fvegetables and away from drinking his
OL,15,Fown beer.
