OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson says doctor told him
OL,4,Cto stop working after heart procedure
OL,6,F"We must now move on to the question
OL,7,Fof exercise," Clarkson added. "I've
OL,8,Falways seen this is something you do
OL,9,Fwhen travelling from the car to the
OL,10,Fpub, or from the lunch table to the
OL,11,Fsitting room.
OL,13,F"But apparently, when I've recovered
OL,14,Ffrom the operation, I must do more."
OL,16,FThe 64-year-old also said that he was
OL,17,Faware that his lifestyle was
OL,18,Funhealthy, and he was unconcerned by
OL,19,Fthe thought of dying, but now wants to
OL,20,Fsee his "grandchildren grow up".
