OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson says doctor told him
OL,4,Cto stop working after heart procedure
OL,6,FHe had revealed his "sudden
OL,7,Fdeterioration" in his health, which
OL,8,Fbrought on symptoms of being "clammy",
OL,9,Fwith a "tightness in my chest", and
OL,10,F"pins and needles in my left arm" in a
OL,11,Fcolumn in The Sunday Times at the
OL,12,Fweekend.
OL,14,FClarkson said he went by ambulance to
OL,15,FJohn Radcliffe Hospital in Oxford,
OL,16,Fwhere after an electrocardiogram
OL,17,F(ECG), blood tests and X-rays along
OL,18,Fwith further checks, he was told that
OL,19,Fone of his arteries was "completely
OL,20,Fblocked and the second of three was
OL,21,Fheading that way".
