OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson says doctor told him
OL,4,Cto stop working after heart procedure
OL,6,FHis doctors told him he was perhaps
OL,7,F"days away" from getting very ill, and
OL,8,Fwas fitted with the stents in around
OL,9,Ftwo hours.
OL,11,FClarkson, who previously quit smoking
OL,12,Fafter contracting pneumonia on holiday
OL,13,Fin Spain, ended his show The Grand
OL,14,FTour on Prime Video along with Richard
OL,15,FHammond and James May last month.
